  <div class="alert alert-info text-center" role="alert">
    To deploy your own copy, refer to this project README, and PLEASE head over to the <a href="https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/getting-started-with-nodejs" class="alert-link">Getting Started on Heroku with Node.js</a>.
  </div>
